{"id":553395,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/03/【对比新闻】淮北乐天玛特员工维权：非新闻-vs-淮/","date":"2017-03-04T08:13:24Z","modified":"2017-03-07T07:31:44Z","title":"【对比新闻】淮北乐天玛特员工维权：非新闻 vs 淮北新闻网","content":"<div id=\"attachment_553396\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/淮北新闻.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-553396\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/淮北新闻.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"421\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/淮北新闻.jpg 1810w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/淮北新闻-300x253.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/淮北新闻-768x647.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/淮北新闻-1024x862.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">《淮北日报》旗下的淮北新闻网官方微博截图</span></p></div>\n<p>2014年4月，淮北乐天玛特突然关门停业，大量员工前去示威，控诉该公司违法解约，后遭到警察驱散。<strong>当时没有任何中国媒体报道过此事。首先<a href=\"http://wickedonna2.tumblr.com/post/81564619341/4%E6%9C%882%E6%97%A5%E5%AE%89%E5%BE%BD%E7%9C%81%E6%B7%AE%E5%8C%97%E5%B8%82%E4%B9%90%E5%A4%A9%E7%8E%9B%E7%89%B9%E8%B6%85%E5%B8%82%E7%99%BE%E4%BD%99%E5%91%98%E5%B7%A5%E5%A0%B5%E8%B7%AF%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E8%B5%94%E5%81%BF%E8%A2%AB%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E9%A9%B1%E6%95%A3%E4%BD%8D%E4%BA%8E%E6%B7%AE%E5%8C%97%E5%B8%82%E4%B8%80%E9%A9%AC%E8%B7%AF%E7%9A%84%E4%B9%90%E5%A4%A9%E7%8E%9B%E7%89%B9%E8%B6%85%E5%B8%824\" target=\"_blank\">记录并公开</a>淮北乐天玛特工人讨薪事件的是曾长期坚持搜集整理中国各地“群体性事件”的<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/tag/%e9%9d%9e%e6%96%b0%e9%97%bb/\" target=\"_blank\">非新闻</a>，<span style=\"color: #ff0000\">该站创办人<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/tag/%e5%8d%a2%e6%98%b1%e5%ae%87/\" target=\"_blank\">卢昱宇</a>其女友<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/tag/%e6%9d%8e%e5%a9%b7%e7%8e%89/\" target=\"_blank\">李婷玉</a>在2016年7月因涉嫌“煽动颠覆国家政权”而被正式批捕。</span></strong></p>\n<p>2017年3月3日，<strong>为了在抵制韩国乐天运动中证明淮北人民“二年多前便洞察一切”，提前“饿死”了当地的乐天玛特</strong>，《淮北日报》旗下的淮北新闻网官方微博成为了第一个提及此事的中国媒体。但这次，<strong>员工上街维权被解读为彻头彻尾的“天道好轮回”的正能量。</strong></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_553397\" style=\"width: 460px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/非新闻.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-553397\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/非新闻.jpg\" width=\"450\" height=\"605\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/非新闻.jpg 1678w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/非新闻-223x300.jpg 223w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/非新闻-768x1033.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/非新闻-762x1024.jpg 762w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">非新闻 推特内容截图</span></p></div>\n<p><strong>附：部分非新闻当时搜集整理的现场图片</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/e4a0da78jw1ef126525sej20dc0hswgy.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-553398\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/e4a0da78jw1ef126525sej20dc0hswgy.jpg\" width=\"375\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/e4a0da78jw1ef126525sej20dc0hswgy.jpg 480w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/e4a0da78jw1ef126525sej20dc0hswgy-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 375px) 100vw, 375px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/66386d63jw1ef103idvnxj20qo0f0wfd.jpeg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-553399\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/66386d63jw1ef103idvnxj20qo0f0wfd.jpeg\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/66386d63jw1ef103idvnxj20qo0f0wfd.jpeg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/66386d63jw1ef103idvnxj20qo0f0wfd-300x169.jpeg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/66386d63jw1ef104io0paj20qo0f075n.jpeg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-553400\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/66386d63jw1ef104io0paj20qo0f075n.jpeg\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/66386d63jw1ef104io0paj20qo0f075n.jpeg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/66386d63jw1ef104io0paj20qo0f075n-300x169.jpeg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/66386d63jw1ef0zy6r9osj20mo0cr3zh.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-553401\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/66386d63jw1ef0zy6r9osj20mo0cr3zh.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/66386d63jw1ef0zy6r9osj20mo0cr3zh.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/66386d63jw1ef0zy6r9osj20mo0cr3zh-300x169.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/e4a0da78jw1ef126n6b57j20dc0hsjtv.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-553402\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/e4a0da78jw1ef126n6b57j20dc0hsjtv.jpg\" width=\"375\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/e4a0da78jw1ef126n6b57j20dc0hsjtv.jpg 480w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/e4a0da78jw1ef126n6b57j20dc0hsjtv-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 375px) 100vw, 375px\" /></a></p>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[32534,31251,32536,32538,31666,21038,8646,9481,26944]}